\c 4
\s Kutambudzika kwavanhu
\s nokuda kwezvivi
\p
\v 4
\v 1 Haiwa, ndarama yasviba sei! Ndarama yakaisvo-naka yashanduka sei!
\s Mabwe enzvimbo tsvene arashirwa pamharadzano dzenzira dzomuguta.
\p
\v 2 Vanakomana vanodikanwa velioni vakafanana nendarama yakaisvo-naka,
\s haiwa vakanzi vakaita sezvirongo zvevhu sei,
\s iro basa romuumbi wehari!
\p
\v 3 Kunyange namakava anobudisa mazamu,
\s achiyamwisa vana vawo;
\s mukunda wavanhu vangu
\s wava nehasha semhou murenje.
\p
\v 4 Rurimi rwomwana unomwa runonatnatira
\s mumukanwa womuromo wake nenyota;
\s vanana vanokumbira chingwa,
\s asi hakuna munhu anovamedurira.
\p
\v 5 Avo vaisidya zvinozipa,
